    "content": "<h2>Magnety</h2>\n<p><strong>Magnet</strong> je těleso, které přitahuje předměty z feromagnetických materiálů (železo, kobalt, nikl).</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;margin:1.5rem auto;max-width:520px;\"><svg viewBox='0 0 460 180' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' style='width:100%;font-family:sans-serif'>\n  <rect x='130' y='65' width='100' height='50' rx='5' fill='#ef4444'/><text x='180' y='95' text-anchor='middle' fill='white' font-weight='bold' font-size='16'>N</text>\n  <rect x='230' y='65' width='100' height='50' rx='5' fill='#3b82f6'/><text x='280' y='95' text-anchor='middle' fill='white' font-weight='bold' font-size='16'>S</text>\n  <path d='M90,90 Q92.5,77.5 95,65' fill='none' stroke='#9ca3af' stroke-width='1' opacity='0.6'/><path d='M95,65 Q100,55 105,45' fill='none' stroke='#9ca3af' stroke-width='1' opacity='0.6'/><path d='M105,45 Q112.5,40 120,35' fill='none' stroke='#9ca3af' stroke-width='1' opacity='0.6'/><path d='M120,35 Q130,35 140,35' fill='none' stroke='#9ca3af' stroke-width='1' opacity='0.6'/><path d='M140,35 Q147.5,40 155,45' fill='none' stroke='#9ca3af' stroke-width='1' opacity='0.6'/><path d='M155,45 Q160,55 165,65' fill='none' stroke='#9ca3af' stroke-width='1' opacity='0.6'/><path d='M165,65 Q167.5,77.5 170,90' fill='none' stroke='#9ca3af' stroke-width='1' opacity='0.6'/><path d='M170,90 Q167.5,102.5 165,115' fill='none' stroke='#9ca3af' stroke-width='1' opacity='0.6'/><path d='M165,115 Q160,125 155,135' fill='none' stroke='#9ca3af' stroke-width='1' opacity='0.6'/><path d='M155,135 Q147.5,140 140,145' fill='none' stroke='#9ca3af' stroke-width='1' opacity='0.6'/><path d='M140,145 Q130,145 120,145' fill='none' stroke='#9ca3af' stroke-width='1' opacity='0.6'/><path d='M120,145 Q112.5,140 105,135' fill='none' stroke='#9ca3af' stroke-width='1' opacity='0.6'/><path d='M105,135 Q100,125 95,115' fill='none' stroke='#9ca3af' stroke-width='1' opacity='0.6'/><path d='M95,115 Q92.5,102.5 90,90' fill='none' stroke='#9ca3af' stroke-width='1' opacity='0.6'/>\n  <text x='80' y='95' fill='#ef4444' font-size='12' text-anchor='middle'>severní pól</text>\n  <text x='380' y='95' fill='#3b82f6' font-size='12' text-anchor='middle'>jižní pól</text>\n  <path d='M130,55 Q60,30 60,90 Q60,150 130,125' fill='none' stroke='#9ca3af' stroke-width='1.5' marker-end='url(#mg)'/>\n  <path d='M130,60 Q80,40 80,90 Q80,140 130,120' fill='none' stroke='#9ca3af' stroke-width='1.5' marker-end='url(#mg)'/>\n  <path d='M330,55 Q400,30 400,90 Q400,150 330,125' fill='none' stroke='#9ca3af' stroke-width='1.5' marker-start='url(#mg)'/>\n  <path d='M330,60 Q380,40 380,90 Q380,140 330,120' fill='none' stroke='#9ca3af' stroke-width='1.5' marker-start='url(#mg)'/>\n  <text x='230' y='25' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='12'>magnetické indukční čáry</text>\n  <defs><marker id='mg' viewBox='0 0 6 6' refX='3' refY='3' markerWidth='4' markerHeight='4' orient='auto'><path d='M0,0 L6,3 L0,6Z' fill='#9ca3af'/></marker></defs>\n</svg></div><h3>Póly magnetu</h3>\n<p>Každý magnet má dva <strong>póly</strong>:</p>\n<table><thead><tr><th>Pól</th><th>Značení</th><th>Barva</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr><td>Severní</td><td>N (north)</td><td>červená</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Jižní</td><td>S (south)</td><td>modrá</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3>Vzájemné působení magnetů</h3>\n<p><strong>Souhlasné póly</strong> (N–N, S–S) se <strong>odpuzují</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Nesouhlasné póly</strong> (N–S) se <strong>přitahují</strong>.</p>\n<h3>Magnetické pole</h3>\n<p>Kolem magnetu existuje <strong>magnetické pole</strong>. Znázorňujeme ho <strong>magnetickými indukčními čarami</strong> — vycházejí ze severního pólu a vcházejí do jižního.</p>\n<h3>Druhy magnetů</h3>\n<p><strong>Přírodní</strong> — magnetovec (magnetit).</p>\n<p><strong>Umělé</strong> — vyrobené z oceli nebo speciálních slitin (permanentní magnety).</p>"
  }
}
